Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.85,0:00:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! You got time on your hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:10.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiz Trial 7
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to\Nbe the quiz king of Kamiyama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:15.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiz Trial 7
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's at least get\Nyou through the preliminary round!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:22.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiz Trial 7
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiz... Trial...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:48.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You hold your breath to make it through\Nthe bewildering day that confronts you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:55.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know what this is, don't you?\NWhat do you want to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:01:01.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The pain from shrugging\Nit all off as nothing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:07.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}urges you on enough to be encouraging{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:14.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Catching hold but making a mess,\Nwe're still inadequate{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:22.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but as long as we can forge\Nour shining, unseen future selves...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:30.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Awaken and run where it takes you,\Nleaving mirages behind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:37.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Run with your desire to change,\Nfrom your comfort zone into freedom{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:44.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Start choosing between now\Nand the brilliance you can attain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:52.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unaware of your destination,\Ndeep breaths following shallow ones{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Corpse By Evening
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Question number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The term "adamant" refers to diamond,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while the term "beryl" refers to emerald.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this true? Or is this false?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that's a decent first question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,true!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show them who the true database is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our numbers are gradually\Ngetting squeezed down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will this be the final question\Nof the preliminary round?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes question number seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The word {\i1}darui {\i0}[listless] derives\Nfrom the English word "dull."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this true? Or is this false?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:02:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, it seems like it ought\Nto be derived from it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Mayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to build it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,False!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That completes the preliminaries!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations to those\Nwho answered correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The championship round will\Nbe held on this platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:29.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Championship Round
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukube, that's an interesting outfit.\NHere's our first finalist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he, again?\NPlease tell us your name and class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, well...\NI'm Shimizu Noriko, Class 3-E.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shimizu Noriko, Class 3-E.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't even notice me here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner will be the first\None to score seven points.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was too focused on the quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I remember now.\NHow do you feel about your chances?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Tani-{\i1}kun{\i0}, how's the Go Club?\NYes, well, I am a little nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? The Go Club?\N\NYes, well, I am a little nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's introduce our\Nsecond finalist. Name and class?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a funny story about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goto Naoki, Class 2-C. I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, our third finalist...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! He has a giant Saturn\Non top of his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name and class, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Fukube Satoshi, of\Nthe Classic Lit Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Classic Lit Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, we have a Classic Lit Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From your outfit, I'd say you have\Nlots of odd club activities, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Yes, odd club activities!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, our goals are not well-defined.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is that right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We knew that creating an anthology\Nwas one of our activities,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we did make one. And if I do\Nsay so myself, it came out awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We put our all into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We put our all into it, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:50.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Goal: Sell out all 200 copies!\N|̶|̶|̶|̶\N|̶|̶|̶|̶ |||
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:50.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,copy-number-wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, we uncovered an important\Nsecret about the Kanyasai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:04:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The origins of the Kanyasai name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kamiyama High School Culture Festival" did\Nnot simply get compressed down to "Kanyasai."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Classic Lit Club has...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,learned the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is the origin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please buy one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For just ¥200, the 45-year-old secret
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of Kamiyama High School's\Nculture festival can be yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our anthology, {\i1}Hyouka{\i0}, is selling fast
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the Earth Science Prep Room, on the\N4th floor of the auxiliary building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pitch successful. I don't care\Nif I win at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Tanabe-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,having them placed at other clubs'\Nlocations will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I tried to go discuss it with\NIrisu-{\i1}san{\i0}, but I never made it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I get the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi's plug was pretty interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Plug?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! As I recall, the Wall Newspaper\NClub is putting out an extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go ask them if they will\Ncover the Classic Lit Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always on the go, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Wall Newspaper Club\NGathering news
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Togaito-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I ask you to cover\Nthe Classic Lit Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I understand what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg your pardon. I came to ask\Nif you would be good enough
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to include an article promoting the\NClassic Lit Club in the wall newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in the club anymore.\NI'm a 3rd-year, so I've retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me. Then would you mind\Nintroducing me to your juniors?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be fine, but I don't\Nthink it will do any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're running a one-page\Nextra in two hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so their lineup is already\Nset up in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's impossible for\Nthem to run anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's some room available on the page
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you can wait until\Nafter noon on Day Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are over 50 organizations\Nwith booths at Kanyasai,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they give priority to\Nthose who merit attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And forgive me for saying so,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the Classic Lit Club is only\Npublishing an anthology, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But the anthology contains...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each club is serious about what it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a story that will\Ngarner everyone's attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask them myself to run\Nan article about it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A story, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Please excuse me\Nfor taking up your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any interesting\Nstories come up, drop by again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be able to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaho-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Uncle Jumonji doing well\Nafter everything that happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100 percent. But never mind him,\Nhow are you? You seem unusually down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a lot going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunetelling Club\NFortunes of every kind Each reading 20 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like, I can read your fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is always so amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... All right,\Nlet's do tarot cards, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm afraid I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eru, you enjoy these, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:15.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fortunetelling Club has already\Nlost its Wheel of Fortune.... Jumonji
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing this all by myself,\Nso I'm away from here quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After stepping out for\Na moment and coming back,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my Wheel of Fortune card\Nwas gone from my tarot deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that card had been left in its place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Jumonji"? Kaho-{\i1}san{\i0}, why is your\Nlast name written on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, why indeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you located the card that disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was left here, too. I\Nthink it will be coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be returned after the culture festival is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a thief, they certainly\Nare strange, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I think I'll show you one last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:55.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting Around at Kanyasai
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there\Nsomething special about that guidebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its pages are the same as\Nthe others going around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was left here together with that card...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,opened to the last page,\Nwith all the club comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does all of this mean anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? As long as I get my\NWheel of Fortune back safely,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, at last, it's our climax!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimizu-{\i1}san {\i0}and Goto-{\i1}san\N{\i0}both have five points.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tani-{\i1}san {\i0}and Fukube-{\i1}san {\i0}have six points,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and both of them are out to clinch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will end up taking it all?\NLet's hear you all cheer them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now for our next question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The formula to determine\Nthe surface area of a sphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is 4πr².
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oho, that was quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:11:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have not yet finished the question;\Nare you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then Shimizu-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nyour answer, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,⁴⁄₃πr ³.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:19.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct\NIncorrect
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Incorrect
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:25.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The formula to determine the\Nsurface area of a sphere is 4πr².
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give the formula\Nto determine its volume.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is ⁴⁄₃πr ³. Nicely done!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimizu-{\i1}san {\i0}is also now one step away,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as we have three contestants\Nwith six points each!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a spectacular dead heat\Ngoing on. Goto-{\i1}san{\i0}, hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now for our next question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamiyama High School's student\Ncouncil president's full name...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Shimizu-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kugayama Muneyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:14.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct\NIncorrect
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to build it up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct\NIncorrect
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:19.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Quiz Trial 7 champion is\NShimizu Noriko, from Class 3-E!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Fukube!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Hey, so close, huh? Both of us.\NThe Quiz Trial 7 champion is\NShimizu Noriko, from Class 3-E!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. I guess it's a draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? What did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To continue that funny story about the Go Club. \NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of our go stones were stolen.\NAll right, the club president\Nwill present you with your prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah? Not lost, but stolen?\NShimizu-{\i1}san{\i0}, please come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a confession note\Nstuck in the go stone bowl,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that said "We've taken some\Ngo stones from the Go Club."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for giving us such\Na well-fought battle today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we use {\i1}all {\i0}of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they could take ten away,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we wouldn't notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would they steal them for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, ladies and gentlemen, the Quiz Club's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, to play Five-in-a-Row, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiz Trial 7...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some other club is goofing with you.\NIs now concluded! Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let this end in a tie between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's settle this! Where are\Nyou competing next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Cooking Club, tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We'll settle this\Nscore for good there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimizu-{\i1}san{\i0}, how do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tacky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in\Ncompeting with Tani-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Hotaro is hard at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You open?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, we're open.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what has the origins\Nof Kanyasai's name in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if I thumb through it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do. It's only ¥200; please buy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got so many of them here, it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, your barn door is open.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, it's torn off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, please try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Oh! I'm surprised you\Nhave one of these! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you. Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An air gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a water pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're roasting sweet potatoes\Nin the Gardening Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using a bucket to put out the\Nfire is so primitive, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:15:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you need this, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just my sidearm.\NMy main weapon is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an AK.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Zat so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, man! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Glock 17, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:19.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shuubun{\i0} ('Middle of Autumn')\NWhen light\Nfindeth equal measure with darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:19.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This collection was doomed from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's coming, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should start making up posters now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,inviting customers in here, I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm. But we all decided that\Nwe would proceed like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they looking at {\i1}me{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Manga Club collection on sale\N100 reviews of manga through the ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100 manga reviews?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna read something\Nas stuffy as that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Kochi-{\i1}san{\i0}, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, there's no point\Nin reviewing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waste of time. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Fuku-{\i1}chan {\i0}will believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really was trying to behave myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, it is\Na waste of time, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a question that has everything\Nto do with the reader.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reader?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All manga starts out being\Nequally entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who the writer is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how do you decide whether\Nor not one is interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know, Ibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to the reader.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimately, it depends on\Nwhether the reader's antenna
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for picking up on entertainment\Nstands high or low, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what you're saying is that those\Nwho have their antennas low
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can't pick up on what's interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why I'm saying\Nthat reviews do no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should just read whatever we like,\Nand have a good laugh over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every manga is the same? That's something\Nyou'll never convince me of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Senpai, by that reasoning,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there would be no such thing as a\Nso-called masterpiece, would there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there {\i1}are {\i0}masterpieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would you define them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those that go on for many years, that manage to\Nhold lots of readers after they sift through them,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are the ones that are masterpieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masterpieces are the ones that are\Ncreated masterpieces from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those that have not stood the test of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're just being\Nsubjective, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a question of experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, you've just never been\Nbowled over by anything
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where you've had to say,\N"This is incredible!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't you the sassy one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's definitely a difference between\Nthe talent and skill of different artists!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did you read the manga that was sold at the\Nschool's culture festival last year that was called
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Corpse By Evening{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll bring it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it still doesn't convince you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I don't have anything left to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just ensured that I won't be able\Nto leave copies of {\i1}Hyouka {\i0}here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle of the Maidens of Manga A\Nheated debate on manga theory
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle of the Maidens?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over now. They will\Ngo at it again tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so by all means, come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you think? About my plug?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it helped at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:37.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,173 copies remaining
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sold 14 copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Publicity works better than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're off to a good start, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll give it another shot tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should do pretty well\Nat the cooking contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the three-man team one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-man teams? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:20:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's on the executive committee, and he\Ndoesn't have a handle on the events?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to increase\Nour number of outlets,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nor was I able to get us covered\Nby the wall newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, there is something\NI'm curious about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm not curious after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm positively thrilled to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it says nothing\Nabout three-man teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No mistake about it. I heard one\Nof the Cooking Club girls say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, I misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could enter on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Mayaka,\Nhow did the Manga Club go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayaka, Chitanda-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would you mind entering the\NCooking Club contest with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can talk to my president\Nto see if she'll let me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it will mean publicity,\NI'd definitely like to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Now at least there's some hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How badly did you want to enter this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fairly proud of my cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I was going\Nto miss a contest this fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention all students,\Nas well as all of our visitors,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this announcement marks the end\Nof the first day of our Kanyasai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those students still in the school,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Oreki-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please lock your doors and make sure\Nall fires are out before leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you, by any chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Nevermind, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.72,0:22:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could it have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:37.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A Corpse By Evening
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.13,0:22:43.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaburaya Middle School Bulletin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.61,0:23:07.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Body Talk
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll bring this, instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.45,0:23:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:44.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Town News Magazine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.45,0:23:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.04,0:23:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.26,0:24:23.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This situation is an unscientific\Nmontage of emotions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.94,0:24:26.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is calling whom?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.61,0:24:32.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your gaze darts away when I turn around\N(I can feel it){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.57,0:24:34.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's unkind to tell me I'm imagining things{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.82,0:24:40.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They say having antennas\Nis a talent, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.33,0:24:45.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I mean I want to know\N(I mean) (don't you?){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.46,0:24:52.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll turn up the heat on your youth\Nfor you now, while there's time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.26,0:24:56.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we can solve this tomorrow,\Nwhy not solve it right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.89,0:25:02.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to solve your mystery{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.48,0:25:07.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Track down that secretive boyish figure!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.19,0:25:14.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Today) you are a fantasy,\Ndrawing me to you, no fair!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.74,0:25:20.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My curiosity is expanding,\Nlack of tricks notwithstanding{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.41,0:25:27.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm fascinated, and I have to know, why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.59,0:25:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Wild Fire."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.93,0:25:43.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild Fire
